    "\"Collective consensus and collaboration.\"",
    "Semantic network regarding the definition of DeSci (created with (Levallois et al., 2012)).",
    "Frontiers in Blockchain frontiersin.org literature review and expert survey, adaptations might be necessary in the future, owing to the rapid advancements in the field of emerging technologies such as DLT and associated developments such as Web3.",
    "Furthermore, the resulting definition of DeSci should be evaluated in the context of the current DeSci ecosystem at the time of this study.",
